{"tid":169623,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"返工有個死八婆分享區","createTime":"2017-03-24T09:53:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-26T18:07:58.000Z","uid":86320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a6f0a8cdf8e4af704f7322b9f3f3f24ea287441e","tid":169623,"uid":86320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T09:53:11.000Z","msg":"小弟分享先<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小弟返工有個大Locker<br />\n唔記得點解岩岩入去做既時候要同兩條女share <br />\n一個locker用，其中一個係八婆黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nLocker我會放啲零食杯麵口痕食下<br />\n仲有一個散銀玻璃樽，同開工用既野。<br />\n<br />\n返左工幾個月都無乜野，冇時發生。<br />\n但小弟去左個旅行，去完返黎，佢笑笑口同我講用曬<br />\n啲散銀，個道應該有七八十蚊左右。<br />\n之後個玻璃樽都係keep住空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 乜玩法<br />\n<br />\n試過買左零食同杯麵放左係locker<br />\n我未食過已經清空左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申:(未試過補倉，一包都冇)<br />\n<br />\n試過佢買左壽司返工食，諗住R佢食一舊都比說話我聽，<br />\n最後係R唔到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n開工用既野大多數都係攞我啲野黎用<br />\n搞到我以為自己唔見咗或冇得用<br />\n利申:(開工裝備須自行購買)<br />\n<br />\n工作表現唔講啦，講到聽日都未講完<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n琴日諗左啲仆街野，打算做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n推到第三頁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d984d897c00e7a445955a635832550624c55a306","tid":169623,"uid":96487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T18:07:58.000Z","msg":"幫樓豬你推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個份咩工黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}